column5: Morning folks, well it looks like fall has arrived after all...I don't know about where you are, but it's chilly up here...  Have a great weekend and stay warm  Maureen
Pretty fresh down here too . . . .    gonna have to drag my fur lined jock from storage for deliverin' the mail today!
chilly here too,actually mentioned the "s" word on the weather
Morning all. 9C here, rain and 17K winds. Same for tomorrow. Going to be 'tween 8C and 12C for the next week or so.
Good morning...  Yep.. Fall has arrived... brrr  You have a good weekend too Mo...
Have a great weekend MO.  It was chilly down here also, fall is on the way big time with also some big fish.

G'day folks  Ole Marv and I just got back in from our daily hike in the woods and it's a gorgeous morning out there, about 8c with clear skies and no wind.  I luv this time of year and will swap 8c for 30c anyday  Hope everyone has a wonderful day, I know I will  !!
